# This directory holds per-template Drupal DB seed dumps used by Approach A of the
# trial site-install optimization (trial-site-install-repo-changes.md).
#
# Files in this directory (seeds/<template>.sql.gz) are generated by the
# "Generate per-template DB seeds for trials" step in .github/workflows/build-artifact.yml
# and committed to the dist branch alongside vendor code.
#
# At runtime, SiteInstallTrialsTask restores the appropriate seed for the selected template
# instead of running a full drush site:install (reduces install time from ~157s to ~5-8s).
#
# DO NOT manually edit or add .sql.gz files here — they are generated by CI only.
# DO NOT add seeds/ to .gitignore in the dist branch.
